---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Leaders">
  <h1>Leaders</h1>

  <p>Leaders is the staff / volunteer-leader directory.</p>
  <h2>Categories</h2>
  <p>Configured via Site Settings → Content → LeaderCategoriesJson (e.g., "Pastoral Staff", "Elders", "Deacons", "Ministry Leaders"). Each leader belongs to one category.</p>
  <h2>Public visibility</h2>
  <p>Leaders are public by default with their photo, name, title, and bio. To hide a leader from the public page without deleting their record, mark them inactive.</p>
</BaseLayout>
